Package: Gmisc
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-12-31
Title: Functions for Descriptive Statistics, Plotting Transitions,
       and More
Author: Max Gordon <max@gforge.se>
Maintainer: Max Gordon <max@gforge.se>
Description: The package contains (1) descriptive and (2) plot functions.
    (1) The descriptive functions generate descriptive statitistics
    aimed at making the "Table 1" used in medical articles.
    (2) The plotting functions included consist of a transition plot,
    an SVD illustration, and bezier arrows for use with the grid package.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: http://gforge.se
BugReports: https://github.com/gforge/Gmisc/issues
Biarch: yes
Depends:
    htmlTable
Imports:
    grid,
    lattice,
    sp,
    Hmisc,
    forestplot
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
Roxygen: list(wrap = TRUE)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
VignetteBuilder: knitr
